[
  {
    "id": 5673,
    "number": 1,
    "key": "78:1",
    "textAr": "عَمَّ يَتَسَآءَلُونَ",
    "textEn": "About what are they asking one another?",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5674,
    "number": 2,
    "key": "78:2",
    "textAr": "عَنِ ٱلنَّبَإِ ٱلْعَظِيمِ",
    "textEn": "About the great news -",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5675,
    "number": 3,
    "key": "78:3",
    "textAr": "ٱلَّذِى هُمْ فِيهِ مُخْتَلِفُونَ",
    "textEn": "That over which they are in disagreement.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5676,
    "number": 4,
    "key": "78:4",
    "textAr": "كَلَّا سَيَعْلَمُونَ",
    "textEn": "No! They are going to know.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5677,
    "number": 5,
    "key": "78:5",
    "textAr": "ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَيَعْلَمُونَ",
    "textEn": "Then, no! They are going to know.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5678,
    "number": 6,
    "key": "78:6",
    "textAr": "أَلَمْ نَجْعَلِ ٱلْأَرْضَ مِهَـٰدًا",
    "textEn": "Have We not made the earth a resting place?",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5679,
    "number": 7,
    "key": "78:7",
    "textAr": "وَٱلْجِبَالَ أَوْتَادًا",
    "textEn": "And the mountains as stakes?",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5680,
    "number": 8,
    "key": "78:8",
    "textAr": "وَخَلَقْنَـٰكُمْ أَزْوَٰجًا",
    "textEn": "And We created you in pairs.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5681,
    "number": 9,
    "key": "78:9",
    "textAr": "وَجَعَلْنَا نَوْمَكُمْ سُبَاتًا",
    "textEn": "And made your sleep [a means for] rest",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5682,
    "number": 10,
    "key": "78:10",
    "textAr": "وَجَعَلْنَا ٱلَّيْلَ لِبَاسًا",
    "textEn": "And made the night as clothing1.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5683,
    "number": 11,
    "key": "78:11",
    "textAr": "وَجَعَلْنَا ٱلنَّهَارَ مَعَاشًا",
    "textEn": "And made the day for livelihood.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5684,
    "number": 12,
    "key": "78:12",
    "textAr": "وَبَنَيْنَا فَوْقَكُمْ سَبْعًا شِدَادًا",
    "textEn": "And constructed above you seven strong [heavens].",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5685,
    "number": 13,
    "key": "78:13",
    "textAr": "وَجَعَلْنَا سِرَاجًا وَهَّاجًا",
    "textEn": "And made [therein] a burning lamp",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5686,
    "number": 14,
    "key": "78:14",
    "textAr": "وَأَنزَلْنَا مِنَ ٱلْمُعْصِرَٰتِ مَآءً ثَجَّاجًا",
    "textEn": "And sent down, from the rain clouds, pouring water.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5687,
    "number": 15,
    "key": "78:15",
    "textAr": "لِّنُخْرِجَ بِهِۦ حَبًّا وَنَبَاتًا",
    "textEn": "That We may bring forth thereby grain and vegetation.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5688,
    "number": 16,
    "key": "78:16",
    "textAr": "وَجَنَّـٰتٍ أَلْفَافًا",
    "textEn": "And gardens of entwined growth.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5689,
    "number": 17,
    "key": "78:17",
    "textAr": "إِنَّ يَوْمَ ٱلْفَصْلِ كَانَ مِيقَـٰتًا",
    "textEn": "Indeed, the Day of Judgement is an appointed time -",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5690,
    "number": 18,
    "key": "78:18",
    "textAr": "يَوْمَ يُنفَخُ فِى ٱلصُّورِ فَتَأْتُونَ أَفْوَاجًا",
    "textEn": "The Day the Horn is blown and you will come forth in multitudes",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5691,
    "number": 19,
    "key": "78:19",
    "textAr": "وَفُتِحَتِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ فَكَانَتْ أَبْوَٰبًا",
    "textEn": "And the heaven is opened and will become gateways.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5692,
    "number": 20,
    "key": "78:20",
    "textAr": "وَسُيِّرَتِ ٱلْجِبَالُ فَكَانَتْ سَرَابًا",
    "textEn": "And the mountains are removed and will be [but] a mirage.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5693,
    "number": 21,
    "key": "78:21",
    "textAr": "إِنَّ جَهَنَّمَ كَانَتْ مِرْصَادًا",
    "textEn": "Indeed, Hell has been lying in wait",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5694,
    "number": 22,
    "key": "78:22",
    "textAr": "لِّلطَّـٰغِينَ مَـَٔابًا",
    "textEn": "For the transgressors, a place of return,",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5695,
    "number": 23,
    "key": "78:23",
    "textAr": "لَّـٰبِثِينَ فِيهَآ أَحْقَابًا",
    "textEn": "In which they will remain for ages [unending].",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5696,
    "number": 24,
    "key": "78:24",
    "textAr": "لَّا يَذُوقُونَ فِيهَا بَرْدًا وَلَا شَرَابًا",
    "textEn": "They will not taste therein [any] coolness or drink.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5697,
    "number": 25,
    "key": "78:25",
    "textAr": "إِلَّا حَمِيمًا وَغَسَّاقًا",
    "textEn": "Except scalding water and [foul] purulence -",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5698,
    "number": 26,
    "key": "78:26",
    "textAr": "جَزَآءً وِفَاقًا",
    "textEn": "An appropriate recompense.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5699,
    "number": 27,
    "key": "78:27",
    "textAr": "إِنَّهُمْ كَانُوا۟ لَا يَرْجُونَ حِسَابًا",
    "textEn": "Indeed, they were not expecting an account",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5700,
    "number": 28,
    "key": "78:28",
    "textAr": "وَكَذَّبُوا۟ بِـَٔايَـٰتِنَا كِذَّابًا",
    "textEn": "And denied Our verses with [emphatic] denial.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5701,
    "number": 29,
    "key": "78:29",
    "textAr": "وَكُلَّ شَىْءٍ أَحْصَيْنَـٰهُ كِتَـٰبًا",
    "textEn": "But all things We have enumerated in writing.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5702,
    "number": 30,
    "key": "78:30",
    "textAr": "فَذُوقُوا۟ فَلَن نَّزِيدَكُمْ إِلَّا عَذَابًا",
    "textEn": "\"So taste [the penalty], and never will We increase you except in torment.\"",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 582,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5703,
    "number": 31,
    "key": "78:31",
    "textAr": "إِنَّ لِلْمُتَّقِينَ مَفَازًا",
    "textEn": "Indeed, for the righteous is attainment -",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 583,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5704,
    "number": 32,
    "key": "78:32",
    "textAr": "حَدَآئِقَ وَأَعْنَـٰبًا",
    "textEn": "Gardens and grapevines.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 583,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5705,
    "number": 33,
    "key": "78:33",
    "textAr": "وَكَوَاعِبَ أَتْرَابًا",
    "textEn": "And full-breasted [companions] of equal age.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 583,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5706,
    "number": 34,
    "key": "78:34",
    "textAr": "وَكَأْسًا دِهَاقًا",
    "textEn": "And a full cup.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 583,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5707,
    "number": 35,
    "key": "78:35",
    "textAr": "لَّا يَسْمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغْوًا وَلَا كِذَّٰبًا",
    "textEn": "No ill speech will they hear therein or any falsehood -",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 583,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5708,
    "number": 36,
    "key": "78:36",
    "textAr": "جَزَآءً مِّن رَّبِّكَ عَطَآءً حِسَابًا",
    "textEn": "[As] reward from your Lord, [a generous] gift [made due by] account,",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 583,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5709,
    "number": 37,
    "key": "78:37",
    "textAr": "رَّبِّ ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ وَمَا بَيْنَهُمَا ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ ۖ لَا يَمْلِكُونَ مِنْهُ خِطَابًا",
    "textEn": "[From] the Lord of the heavens and the earth and whatever is between them, the Most Merciful. They possess not from Him [authority for] speech.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 583,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5710,
    "number": 38,
    "key": "78:38",
    "textAr": "يَوْمَ يَقُومُ ٱلرُّوحُ وَٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ صَفًّا ۖ لَّا يَتَكَلَّمُونَ إِلَّا مَنْ أَذِنَ لَهُ ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنُ وَقَالَ صَوَابًا",
    "textEn": "The Day that the Spirit [i.e., Gabriel] and the angels will stand in rows, they will not speak except for one whom the Most Merciful permits, and he will say what is correct.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 583,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5711,
    "number": 39,
    "key": "78:39",
    "textAr": "ذَٰلِكَ ٱلْيَوْمُ ٱلْحَقُّ ۖ فَمَن شَآءَ ٱتَّخَذَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّهِۦ مَـَٔابًا",
    "textEn": "That is the True [i.e., certain] Day; so he who wills may take to his Lord a [way of] return.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 583,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5712,
    "number": 40,
    "key": "78:40",
    "textAr": "إِنَّآ أَنذَرْنَـٰكُمْ عَذَابًا قَرِيبًا يَوْمَ يَنظُرُ ٱلْمَرْءُ مَا قَدَّمَتْ يَدَاهُ وَيَقُولُ ٱلْكَافِرُ يَـٰلَيْتَنِى كُنتُ تُرَٰبًۢا",
    "textEn": "Indeed, We have warned you of an impending punishment on the Day when a man will observe what his hands have put forth and the disbeliever will say, \"Oh, I wish that I were dust!\"",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 583,
    "hizb": 59
  }
]